169
00:11:54,718 --> 00:11:56,037
Because you've never been frank.

170
00:12:00,637 --> 00:12:01,958
Do you know saving me

171
00:12:02,838 --> 00:12:04,397
will bring disaster to Xue family?

172
00:12:04,797 --> 00:12:06,358
The Xue family has suffered a lot.

173
00:12:07,797 --> 00:12:08,558
But we

174
00:12:09,157 --> 00:12:10,677
won't abandon those in need.

175
00:12:11,238 --> 00:12:12,478
Everyone has

176
00:12:13,198 --> 00:12:14,397
to look out for themselves.

177
00:12:14,637 --> 00:12:16,797
