196
00:13:26,598 --> 00:13:28,797
(If Feng Zuoren hadn't caused trouble,)

197
00:13:29,358 --> 00:13:31,198
(letting Hua Biliang escape,)

198
00:13:31,917 --> 00:13:34,198
(I'd never have tracked him down.)

199
00:13:34,958 --> 00:13:37,598
(Now that Xue Hexu
gave me the painting,)

200
00:13:37,757 --> 00:13:39,797
(it's time to use him.)

201
00:13:40,917 --> 00:13:42,598
(With this person here,)

202
00:13:43,037 --> 00:13:45,677
